This paper deals with the detection of spam campaigns on Twitter using botnets, which involves aspects of social media analysis, cybersecurity, and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.SD (Software Engineering), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
